{"prompt": "Create an inviting website for a personal chef service. The layout should feature a warm saffron orange.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Gourmet Creations - Personal Chef Services</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f8f4f0;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.7), rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.7)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504674904228-964d9f959f61?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80');\n            background-size: cover;\n            background-position: center;\n            height: 600px;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #fff;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        .hero-text {\n            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n            padding: 40px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 4em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: #fff;\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            color: #fff;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 50px auto;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            align-items: flex-start;\n        }\n        .section {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            width: 45%;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            border-left: 5px solid #FF8C00;\n        }\n        h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #FF8C00;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .service-item {\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            padding-bottom: 20px;\n            border-bottom: 1px dashed #ccc;\n        }\n        .service-item:last-child {\n            border-bottom: none;\n        }\n        .service-item h3 {\n            color: #FF8C00;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .contact-form {\n            width: 100%;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .contact-form input, .contact-form textarea {\n            width: 90%;\n            padding: 15px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n        }\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: #FF8C00;\n            color: white;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n        }\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #e67e00;\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px;\n            background-color: #FF8C00;\n            color: white;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 3em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.5em;\n            }\n            .container {\n                width: 90%;\n            }\n            .section {\n                width: 100%;\n                margin-bottom: 20px;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"hero-text\">\n            <h1>Gourmet Creations</h1>\n            <p>Your personal chef for unforgettable culinary experiences.</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"section\">\n            <h2>About Our Service</h2>\n            <p>At Gourmet Creations, we believe that every meal should be an occasion. Our passion is to bring restaurant-quality dining into the comfort of your own home. We specialize in crafting personalized menus tailored to your tastes, dietary needs, and special events. From intimate dinners to lively gatherings, let us elevate your next culinary experience.</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Private Dining</h3>\n                <p>Enjoy bespoke multi-course meals prepared in your home for you and your guests.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Event Catering</h3>\n                <p>Customized menus for parties, anniversaries, and other celebrations.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Meal Prep</h3>\n                <p>Healthy, delicious, and ready-to-eat meals prepared weekly to fit your lifestyle.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"section contact-form\">\n            <h2>Book Your Culinary Experience</h2>\n            <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <input type=\"tel\" name=\"phone\" placeholder=\"Your Phone Number\">\n                <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Tell us about your event or needs\" rows=\"5\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Inquiry</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Gourmet Creations. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}